鸫","body":"不，其实……\n之前小巴因为感冒而倒下了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鸫","body":"虽然想为小巴做些什么\n但是她说要是探病时被传染就不好了\n所以被她拒绝了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鸫","body":"那个时候，一听说小沙绫说要去给小巴送慰问品。\n我就没忍住，\n也送去了慰问品","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鸫","body":"我送去的礼物吗？\n是生姜红茶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"memorial159-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鸫","body":"生姜红茶\n可以让身体暖和起来，\n我觉得正适合感冒的时候喝","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[